{"tid":2460791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門究竟犯咗咩錯？","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:31:48.000Z","uid":44285,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9c0fbc0272d04b69387f0a678d9f2b516a19e8","tid":2460791,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVQDG5XPmBLkRF8JUepxViYTeNYf7uzHnF7S5brPCWbzo?filename=YH4ZE7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYH4ZE7x.jpg&h=fb25a1c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝有嚟食早餐嘅客人可能會知道...<br />\n執達吏到咗尖沙咀店...<br />\n可能7日後就係瓏門嘅最後一日...<br />\n<br />\n瓏門無論做咩都會被評論<br />\n我一直以為清者自清<br />\n與其花時間去內鬥<br />\n不如做好食物出品<br />\n<br />\n生意受謠言影響每況越下<br />\n加上疫情、停晚市堂食<br />\n相信飲食業內都無一倖免<br />\n<br />\n我冇能力改變香港<br />\n只希望可以為運動付出嘅年青人做一D嘢<br />\n所以我喺餐廳生意最好嘅時候去咗攪資源中心<br />\n<br />\n我承認我係喺運動中最失敗的生意人<br />\n直至宜家不但冇車冇樓銀行冇錢<br />\n甚至連一班伙記生計都可能維持唔到<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位一直支持<br />\n無論7日後瓏門存在與否<br />\n我永遠都會記得同大家行過呢一段路<br />\n亦希望大家記得瓏門改好咗嘅味道<br />\n<br />\n對唔住思緒好混亂<br />\n張俊傑（2021年4月1日減7日）"},{"pid":"c6ba47aee573c45c886f4d1b54a9615f232c4ab2","tid":2460791,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"龍門是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffa86a7feaf82d2d0b56b642b7dc0f6987e6524","tid":2460791,"uid":38548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c6ba47aee573c45c886f4d1b54a9615f232c4ab2","tid":2460791,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"龍門是原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"個個龍門post 你都係第一個走出黎批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015c20f2b65ac52e75447f8144a019853e1ee187","tid":2460791,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:06:59.000Z","msg":"食過一次<br 